Package com.example.lapum.paclouie

Package info file.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutActivity
    Activity to display game rules.
    ColdStartSimulation
    This class is only to simulate a cold start; delete this class and 'android:name=".ColdStartSimulation"' in AndroidManifest.xml.
    DifficultyActivity
    Difficulty activity handles three button clicks for the three game difficulty.
    GameActivity
    The PacLouie game activity; view and logic to play the game.
    HighscoreActivity
    Activity to display the PacLouie's highscores.
    Louie
    Class to create Louie character.
    MainActivity
    Home screen activity.
    Professor
    Class to create the games professors.
    SettingsActivity
    Class to display the settings page where the number of profs can be modified.
    SplashActivity
    Opening class to display the start screen activity.
    StartScreenActivity
    This class is the "press to start" opening screen.
